{"tid":2068203,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有冇人覺得支藍白「香港旗」配色好似芬蘭國旗？","createTime":"2020-06-17T13:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T03:44:17.000Z","uid":120678,"like":15,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2548b91fe1cbb7f2a30310215f7550f5e6975f18","tid":2068203,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T13:34:38.000Z","msg":"藍白「香港旗」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBws12p.jpg&amp;h=2da0e034&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n芬蘭國旗<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thoughtco.com/thmb/vRtRKEgIZfdsTCwC1EuI2NjTtBk=/768x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(webp)/the-finnish-flag-832493416-5c7550124cedfd0001de0ab7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thoughtco.com%2Fthmb%2FvRtRKEgIZfdsTCwC1EuI2NjTtBk%3D%2F768x0%2Ffilters%3Ano_upscale%28%29%3Amax_bytes%28150000%29%3Astrip_icc%28%29%3Aformat%28webp%29%2Fthe-finnish-flag-832493416-5c7550124cedfd0001de0ab7.jpg&h=cca691dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分別係藍白「香港旗」用烏克蘭旗式設計，芬蘭國旗用Scandinavian Cross<br />\n不過芬蘭用Scandinavian Cross係因為同其他北歐國家+基督教既深厚淵源<br />\n香港唔係基督教國家，冇理由用十字旗設計"},{"pid":"e5995f59a5ab684a3887c5f18b84fac96944a6d0","tid":2068203,"uid":135390,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T13:38:00.000Z","msg":"你不如話三隻色間條個堆好似樣..<br />\n利申一支旗都唔識分"},{"pid":"83ba9886380dd814b3080d6017dce25cbb23ba15","tid":2068203,"uid":280648,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T13:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁好難又唔撞"},{"pid":"1ab4e2297111cf4176f8cb3866035ad48dfbc2f5","tid":2068203,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":27,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T18:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEsoLLj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F